</h1>
<p>
<seg id="2">Germany has chosen the abstention during the vote on the admission of the Palestinian State.</seg>
<seg id="3">According to Stephen Szabo, expert of the relationships between the United States and the EU, this decision puts Berlin in a delicate political situation.</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id="4">Deutsche Welle: At the beginning of the week, Germany had announced his intention of voting against the request for the Palestinian ones of obtaining the statute from observant State next to the United Nations.</seg>
<seg id="5">But she has chosen the abstention afterwards.</seg>
<seg id="6">Why?</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id="7">Stephen Szabo: Germany does not approve it that the Israelis have made to Gassed.</seg>
