<seg id="50">It is not simple for Germany, notably because of the relationships with Israel.</seg>
<seg id="51">This question has always been delicate.</seg>
<seg id="52">But according to me, the Germans are pretty conscious of the fact that they must play a role that marks their independence more.</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id="53">Does Germany see itself play a role of actor of weight on the international scene, does Germany want to accept only a key role?</seg>
